{"arkId":"cl010113108","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113108","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"L\u0027Asie","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"L\u0027Asie"},{"type":"Titre d\u0027usage","value":"Tapisserie \u00e0 l\u0027\u00e9l\u00e9phant"},{"type":"Autre titre","value":"Tapis \u00e0 l\u0027\u00e9l\u00e9phant"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Monarchie de Juillet (1830-1848) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque contemporaine)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1844","currentLocation":"Aubusson (France), Cit\u00e9 internationale de la tapisserie et de l\u0027art tiss\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1844,"endYear":"","imprecision":"","text":"2e quart du XIXe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Sallandrouze, Alexis","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"11\/04\/1802","place":"","type":"date de naissance"}],"creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"Couder, Am\u00e9d\u00e9e","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"Attribu\u00e9 \u00e0","dates":[{"date":"1797","place":"Paris","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1864","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Dessinateur","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""},{"label":"Sallandrouze de Lamornaix, Charles-Jean","attributionLevel":"Ancienne Attribution","linkType":"","creatorRole":"","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":"Q2960180"}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 11775","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"tapis ; tapisserie","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"\u0022Des colonnes torsad\u00e9es jumel\u00e9es soutiennent un arc en accolade, \u00e0 cl\u00e9 pendante. L\u0027encadrement est d\u0027une grande richesse ornementale. Une arcature cr\u00e9nel\u00e9e sert de soubassement avec, au centre, un combat tournoyant d\u0027oiseaux fantastiques. Un r\u00e9seau dense et complexe d\u0027entrelacs, inscrit dans des compartiments vari\u00e9s, meuble tout le restant de cet encadrement, \u00e0 la fa\u00e7on des stucs ou des bois sculpt\u00e9s des architectures islamiques (notamment les \u00e9toiles des \u00e9coin\u00e7ons). De part et d\u0027autre de la sc\u00e8ne centrale, en haut, une niche sert d\u0027\u00e9crin \u00e0 un vase fleuri, \u00e0 demi d\u00e9voil\u00e9 par un store gracieusement \u00e9cart\u00e9 ; un macaque, menac\u00e9 par un ara, tente d\u0027atteindre la niche de gauche, d\u0027o\u00f9 pend une grande branche fleurie. Toute cette architecture s\u0027ouvre sur un lumineux jardin paradisiaque, au centre duquel tr\u00f4ne un \u00e9l\u00e9phant d\u0027Asie, somptueusement par\u00e9 ; l\u0027\u00e9l\u00e9phant porte un palanquin, dans lequel est nonchalamment allong\u00e9 une femme, v\u00eatue \u00e0 l\u0027orientale et munie d\u0027un \u00e9ventail de plumes. De souples guirlandes fleuries, o\u00f9 sont perch\u00e9s des oiseaux de paradis, sont suspendues au-dessus du pachyderme, flanqu\u00e9 \u00e0 gauche d\u0027un bananier, et \u00e0 droite d\u0027un coctier. Une luxuriante v\u00e9g\u00e9tation exotique, pr\u00e9cis\u00e9ment d\u00e9crite, couvre le sol. A gauche, un paon consid\u00e8re la sc\u00e8ne.\u0022 (Dion-Tenenbaum, juin 1995)","inscriptions":"","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Longueur","value":"716","displayDimension":"716 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Hauteur","value":"568","displayDimension":"568 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau\/Technique : fils m\u00e9talliques (trames)\r\nTechnique : tapisserie = tapisserie sur m\u00e9tier (techniques textile) (tapisserie tiss\u00e9e \u0022\u00e0 la monte\u0022)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : coton (chaine)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laine (trames)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : soie (trames)","placeOfCreation":"Aubusson (Limousin-\u003ECreuse)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"A partir de 1935, jusqu\u0027en 1953, au plus tard, pr\u00eat\u00e9 par le grand magasin \u0022A la place de Clichy\u0022 au mus\u00e9e de la France d\u0027outre-mer, et expos\u00e9 dans le hall d\u0027honneur ; galerie Carlton Hobbs, Londres ; don de la Fondation Simone et Cino del Duca \u00e0 l\u0027occasion de son vingti\u00e8me anniversaire, 1995","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"09\/03\/1995","startYear":1995,"endYear":1995},{"type":"date du conseil","value":"15\/03\/1995","startYear":1995,"endYear":1995},{"type":"date de l\u0027arr\u00eat\u00e9\/d\u00e9cision","value":"04\/04\/1995","startYear":1995,"endYear":1995}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"Cit\u00e9 internationale de la tapisserie, Aubusson","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don"}],"period":[{"value":"Monarchie de Juillet (1830-1848)"}],"place":[{"value":"Aubusson"}],"objectType":[{"value":"tapis"},{"value":"tapisserie"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Dion-Tenenbaum, Anne, \u00ab \u0022Aubusson et l\u0027Asie\u0022 \u00bb, L\u0027estampille\/L\u0027objet d\u0027art, 292, juin 1995, p. 62-67","bibliographyDate":"juin 1995","bibliographyDetail":"p. 63-67, ill. p. 62-63, 64, 65, 66, 67","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Sallandrouze de Lamornaix 1801 1878 : hi